<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The A17 is used when it is decided that two patients will exchange beds. The patient ID and visit data are repeated for the two patients changing places. See section <a href="#swapping-a-patient"><em>3.6.1</em></a>, "<em><a href="#swapping-a-patient">Swapping a patient</a>,</em>" for a discussion of issues related to implementing this trigger event. When other important fields change, it is recommended that the A08 (update patient information) event be used in addition.</p>
</div>
